div.p:
. . . unto the bishop of the church, and unto such as God shall appoint and ordain to watch over the church and to be elders unto the church, are to have it given unto them to discern all those gifts lest there shall be any among you professing and yet be not of God.
And it shall come to pass that he that asketh in Spirit shall receive in Spirit;
That unto some it may be given to have all those gifts, that there may be a head in order that every member may be profited thereby (D&C 46:27-29).
